	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Mobile</placeName> <date>May 2nd 1853</date></p>
				<p>Dear friend&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Enclosed you will find <persName>St John Paverski<add>&#63;</add></persName><lb/> check on Bk N. America your favor for<lb/> Three hundred &#38; fifty Dols. &#40;&#36;350&#41;&#8212;the<lb/> odd fifty you will please dispose of as<lb/> follows&#8212;Six Dols. To <persName>Geo &#38; Jas Benners</persName> the<lb/> liquor men in <placeName>2nd below Race St.</placeName> to cover<lb/> a small balance of that Amt. against me.<lb/>  Thirty five 30&#47;100 Dols&#8212;please pay to <persName>Wm<lb/> Hoskins</persName> when he calls on you for it.  I<lb/> shall draw on you in his favor for the<lb/> amt. So as not to trouble you to go to him.<lb/>  <persName>Hoskins</persName> is the man who made my Dray<lb/> the balance of the fifty&#59; Eight 70&#47;100 please hand<lb/> to <persName>Mrs O.</persName> to get <persName>Nell</persName> a dress or any article of<lb/> clothing she may prefer.  The Rest of the<lb/> check you know about from my letter<lb/> last night.  I have nothing to add to<lb/> it but beg you not to forget the &#8220;two bad<lb/> paymasters&#8222; I have invariably found payment in<lb/> advance to be detrimental to both parties&#8212;but<lb/> prompt payment as the work is done will<lb/> secure you willing workmen &#38; good work.<lb/>  With my <sic>sincer</sic> love and assurances of<lb/> my constant good wishes for your health<lb/> &#38; prosperity Believe me Ever yr friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">SWolff</persName>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philad</placeName></p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>I would have added to the within the<lb/> amt due you from <persName>Jones</persName> congregation<lb/> but have not collected it yet&#8212;I miss<lb/> him every time I go there &#38; when we<lb/> meet we <sic>cant</sic> get hold of the Sec.<lb/> it shall come along shortly though</p>
		</body>
